/span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tax.ohio.gov/portals/0/taxeducation/history/taxation%20in%20ohio_history.pdf\">\"Taxation in Ohio: History of Major Changes\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <i>Ohio Department of Taxation</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">6 October</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Ohio+Department+of+Taxation&amp;rft.atitle=Taxation+in+Ohio%3A+History+of+Major+Changes&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tax.ohio.gov%2Fportals%2F0%2Ftaxeducation%2Fhistory%2Ftaxation%2520in%2520ohio_history.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMiller+v.+Korns\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Alexander, Kern; Alexander, M. (2012). <i>American Public School Law</i> (8th ed.). California: Wadsworth, Cengage Learning. p.&#160;1068. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-495-91049-7\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-495-91049-7\">978-0-495-91049-7</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=American+Public+School+Law&amp;rft.place=California&amp;rft.pages=1068&amp;rft.edition=8th&amp;rft.pub=Wadsworth%2C+Cengage+Learning&amp;rft.date=2012&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-495-91049-7&amp;rft.aulast=Alexander&amp;rft.aufirst=Kern&amp;rft.au=Alexander%2C+M.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMiller+v.+Korns\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_n